#. module: metal_fabricator
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:metal_fabricator.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Adjust the <b>scheduled date</b> (when you plan to start) and the "
"<b>deadline</b> (when it needs to be completed, based on the Sales Order's "
"delivery date)."
msgstr ""
"<b>予定日</b> (開始予定日) と<b>期限</b> (販売オーダの納期に基づいて、いつま"
